Note on cultural content
------------------------

The dictionary bundled at `docs/dictionary.yaml` is sourced verbatim from the
community-managed repository at https://github.com/australia/mobtranslate.com
and records the Kuku Yalanji language of the Kuku Yalanji people of Far
North Queensland, Australia.  That content is NOT our intellectual property
to relicense.  The MIT licence above covers the source code in this
repository; the dictionary file remains under whatever terms the upstream
project applies, and its cultural stewardship belongs to the Kuku Yalanji
community.

This project is a research artefact.  For teaching, speaking, or cultural
use of Kuku Yalanji, go to the Kuku Yalanji people and their teachers, not
this code.
